Movie: This House Has People in It

Review: Probably the best project Snyder has ever worked on.
"huh. so it's for tv?" "i think so."
Such a fun, spooky, and terribly eerie movie. Argentinian horror is something I’m so very excited to delve deeper in.
A bit by the numbers, but the numbers are inflated with a shocking amount of blood.
So warm and cozy. Like a blanket.
So incredibly moving and so kind hearted.
I love the third act but the first still isn’t clicking
